function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

--Destroy Traps
tTraps = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Scos_Highlands_APyreofAsh_Traps")
	for i, idTrap in ipairs(tTraps) do
		Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idTrap, 1.0)
	end
--Enable Ambush Bandits
tBandits = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorGizmo, "Bandits")
	for i, idBandit in ipairs(tBandits) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(idBandit)
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idBandit, false)
		Hydra.QActorPower(idBandit, "Summoned_Animating_Ceiling")
	end
Hydra.Wait(2.0)
--Enable Torben, entrance
Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_TORBEN_01)
Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_TORBEN_01, LOC_ENTRANCE, "NPC_Walk", true)
--Initiate Conversation/Enable Torben
Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CON_AMBUSH, ID_MILITANT, false, ID_TORBEN_01)
Hydra.Wait(1.0)
--Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_TORBEN_01)
Hydra.Wait(1.0)
for i, idBandit in ipairs(tBandits) do
		Hydra.QActorFaceActor(idBandit, ID_TORBEN_01)
	end
Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(CON_AMBUSH)

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

--Enable Ambush Bandits
tBandits = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(GIZ_PYRE, "Bandits")
	for i, idBandit in ipairs(tBandits) do
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idBandit, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetNoDamage(idBandit, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idBandit, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idBandit, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_0)
	end

end

function Start(idActorKiller, szGroup)
	
--Move Torben to Pyre
	followerTorben = Hydra.QuestGetFollowers()[1]
	
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerTorben, false)
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerTorben)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CON_BARK_BODIES, followerTorben)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerTorben, LOC_PYRE, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerTorben, LOC_PYRE)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(followerTorben, CON_BARK_BODIES)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerTorben)
	Hydra.ActorSetSheathPreference(followerTorben, (Hydra.SHEATH_PREF_SHEATHED))
	Hydra.Wait(1.0)
	Hydra.EventSend("PyreChat")
	
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

--Torben exiting Conversation
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CON_BARK_EXIT, ID_TORBEN_02)
	Hydra.QActorSetConversationStatus(ID_TORBEN_02, false)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_TORBEN_02, LOC_ENTRANCE, "NPC_Walk", true)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_TORBEN_02, CON_BARK_EXIT)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ID_TORBEN_02, 1.0)
	
end
